ior Mechanical Engineer · R&amp;D Department</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"block font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Full Name</label>\n<input class=\"w-full p-3 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition-all\" type=\"text\" value=\"Zhang Wei\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"block font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Professional Title</label>\n<input class=\"w-full p-3 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition-all\" type=\"text\" value=\"Senior Engineer\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"block font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Department</label>\n<input class=\"w-full p-3 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition-all\" type=\"text\" value=\"R&amp;D / Industrial Automation\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"block font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Mobile Number</label>\n<input class=\"w-full p-3 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition-all\" type=\"tel\" value=\"+86 138-xxxx-8888\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"md:col-span-2 space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"block font-label-md text-on-surface-variant\">Email Address</label>\n<input class=\"w-full p-3 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary outline-none transition-all\" type=\"email\" value=\"wei.zhang@industrial-tech.com\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-8 flex justify-end\">\n<button class=\"px-8 py-2.5 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors shadow-sm active:scale-95\">Save Changes</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- Section: Contacts -->\n<section cl