"text-body-sm\">New Quote Alerts</span>\n<input class=\"rounded text-primary focus:ring-primary h-5 w-5\" type=\"checkbox\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-4\">\n<h4 class=\"font-label-md text-on-surface font-bold\">Appearance</h4>\n<div class=\"space-y-3\">\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"block text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">Language</label>\n<select class=\"w-full p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant text-body-sm outline-none\">\n<option>Simplified Chinese</option>\n<option>English (United States)</option>\n<option>Deutsch (German)</option>\n</select>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-2\">\n<label class=\"block text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">Theme Mode</label>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2\">\n<button class=\"flex-1 py-2 rounded-lg border border-primary bg-primary-container text-white font-bold text-[12px]\">Light</button>\n<button class=\"flex-1 py-2 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant text-on-surface-variant font-bold text-[12px] hover:bg-surface\">Dark</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"px-8 pb-8 flex justify-end\">\n<button class=\"px-8 py-2.5 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors shadow-sm\">Save Preferences</button>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"h-16\"></div>"
